{"tid":241963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又係電騙】男商人北上見「女公安」 失136萬人仔","createTime":"2017-05-13T14:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T02:41:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e65821e59e5322b4e0a77d9469c0b4e9101a64cf","tid":241963,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170513/large/1494671567_101e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170513%2Flarge%2F1494671567_101e.jpg&h=ed36ff40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 【22:00 更新】事主為商人，早前騙徒安排一名假冒女公安與他會面，博取信任<br />\n<br />\n大嶼山愉景灣一名54歲男商人，早前接獲一名陌生男子來電，對方自稱為入境處人員，並指他涉嫌與一宗刑事案件有關，電話其後轉駁至另一名自稱是上海公安的男子。事主按指示登入一個網站填寫銀行戶口資料以協助調查，其後更到深圳安排與一名自稱是女公安見面。事主其後發現戶口內有共約136萬元人民幣被提走，懷疑受騙，至今早10時許報案。警方經初步調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由大嶼山警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進，暫沒有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170513/56689777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170513%2F56689777&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f335e895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170513%2F56689777&h=28b9877d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170513/56689777</a>"},{"pid":"21cb9ffa6906b4ac8d747152a7286822ce5fc20f","tid":241963,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5139cc9a892f0321e4f4eca133cc9fda011f2737","tid":241963,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:42:38.000Z","msg":"大陸匪真係聰明，專做同胞世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12aea555d5a86fb2934af8699b8f8548802ffa97","tid":241963,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,